channel.title: How did your name come to be?
channel.description:
How did you get your name on moparisthebest's forums? Post and tell your story.
I got my because I just found out about private servers and was soo excited. I was on this one private server with the name 3 hit u. Some guy thought it was the real 3 hit u and started complimenting me and stuff, and gave me an account on that server, called [b]Pko[/b]. Right after that, I registered with it, and now I'm stuck with it.
